@startuml

title Notifier Component Diagram

!define TASK_COLOR #LightBlue
!define QUEUE_COLOR #LightGreen

component [Notifier Task] as Notifier TASK_COLOR

queue "Queue 1" as Q1 QUEUE_COLOR
queue "Queue 2" as Q2 QUEUE_COLOR
queue "Queue 3" as Q3 QUEUE_COLOR

component [Syncjob Task A] as TaskA TASK_COLOR
component [Syncjob Task B] as TaskB TASK_COLOR
component [Syncjob Task C] as TaskC TASK_COLOR

Notifier --> Q1 : tx
Notifier --> Q2 : tx
Notifier --> Q3 : tx

Q1 --> TaskA : rx
Q2 --> TaskB : rx
Q3 --> TaskC : rx


note right of Notifier
    Central task that publishes
    notifications to multiple mpsc queues
end note

note top of Q3
    Each mpsc queue is consumed
    by exactly one task
end note

@enduml